## 🎯 1. Product Overview (Ye Kya Hai?)

**Media Hoster** ek enterprise-grade, serverless **Video-on-Demand (VOD) streaming platform** hai jo teen major technologies ko milake kaam karta hai:

1. **WordPress** — Content publish karne ki jagah (tumhara main blog/website)
2. **Next.js on Vercel** — Backend server jahan database aur authentication hai
3. **Cloudflare Worker** — Edge streaming engine jo video deliver karta hai

### Core Philosophy (Kyun Banaya?)

> **Problem:** Agar tum apni WordPress post mein seedha video ka link daalo (YouTube, Videy, etc.), toh:
> - Google AdX reviewer us link ko dekh sakta hai → **Ad disapproval**
> - Competitors tumhara video source chura sakte hain
> - Direct links scrape ho sakte hain → **Bandwidth theft**
> - Video CDN ka URL visitors ko pata chal jata hai

> **Solution:** Ek aisi system jahan WordPress post mein sirf ek **8-character UUID** hota hai (jaise `a1b2c3d4`). Asli video ka link sirf backend database mein chhipa hota hai. User jab play button press karta hai tab ek **cryptographic token** banta hai jiske zariye Cloudflare Worker video stream karta hai — bina asli URL kabhi expose kiye.

