## 🏛️ 2. System Architecture (Poora System Kaise Bana Hai?)

```
[ Visitor Browser ]
      │
      ├──(1) Page Load ─────────────────────────────▶ [ WordPress Site ]
      │                                                      │
      │                                              (Bot check karein)
      │                                                      │
      ├──(2) Fetch Thumbnail ◀───────────────────────────────┤
      │
      ├──(3) Play Click + Token Request ───────────▶ [ Next.js Backend ]
      │                                               (Vercel Serverless)
      │                                               DB → HMAC Token
      │
      ├──(4) Token URL ◀────────────────────────────────────-┘
      │      (Cloudflare Worker URL + encrypted token)
      │
      ├──(5) Stream Request ────────────────────────▶ [ Cloudflare Worker ]
      │                                                (Edge - Global CDN)
      │                                                Token verify + fetch
      │
      ├──(6) Video Chunks 206 Partial ◀────────────────────--┤
      │      (Zero-Copy, Range-aware streaming)
      ▼
[ Video plays! No buffering. Source URL never exposed. ]
```

