```

#### Table: `Video`
```sql
id                  INT          PRIMARY KEY AUTO_INCREMENT
video_uuid          VARCHAR(255) UNIQUE   -- 8-char hex (e.g., "a1b2c3d4")
title               VARCHAR(255)          -- Human readable title
thumbnail_path      TEXT                  -- Public CDN URL of thumbnail
original_source_url TEXT                  -- ⚠️ HIDDEN: Actual video URL
