### Component 2B: Authentication System

#### Signup Flow:
```
POST /api/auth/signup { username, email, password }
  → Check: username/email exists?
  → bcrypt.hash(password, 10) → password_hash
  → crypto.randomBytes(24).toString('hex') → api_token (48 chars)
  → DB mein save (User table)
  → 201 Created
```

#### Login Flow:
```
POST /api/auth/login { identifier, password, rememberMe }
  → DB se user fetch by username OR email
  → bcrypt.compare(password, hash) → match?
  → jwt.sign({ userId, username }, JWT_SECRET, { expiresIn: rememberMe ? '30d' : '24h' })
  → HTTP-Only Cookie: auth_token = <jwt>
  → 200 OK → Redirect to homepage
```

#### Session Check:
```
GET /api/auth/me (Cookie: auth_token = <jwt>)
  → jwt.verify(cookie, JWT_SECRET) → { userId }
  → DB se user: { id, username, email, api_token }
  → 200 OK (api_token bhi diya profile page ke liye)
```

#### Forgot Password Flow:
```
POST /api/auth/forgot-password { email }
  → 4-digit code: Math.floor(1000 + Math.random() * 9000)
  → DB mein save: reset_code, reset_code_expires (now + 15 min)
  → Nodemailer email: "Your code is: 1234"

POST /api/auth/reset-password { email, code, newPassword }
  → DB check: code match + not expired?
  → bcrypt.hash(newPassword) → update DB
  → reset_code = null
```

