### Component 2C: Media API — The Token Issuer (`/api/media`)

#### Action 1: `get_thumb`
```
GET /api/media?action=get_thumb&uuid=a1b2c3d4
  Step 1: Redis cache check → redis.get('video_meta:a1b2c3d4')
  Step 2 (cache miss): MySQL fetch WHERE video_uuid = 'a1b2c3d4'
  Step 3: Redis mein cache karo (EX 3600 = 1 hour)
  Response: { success: true, thumbnail: "https://r2.dev/thumb.jpg" }
```

> **Redis Caching:** Ek baar DB hit ke baad agle 1 ghante tak har request Redis se serve hogi. High traffic mein MySQL overload nahi hogi.

#### Action 2: `get_stream` (Most Important!)
```
GET /api/media?action=get_stream&uuid=a1b2c3d4
  Step 1: Video fetch (Redis/MySQL)
  Step 2: Token expiry = now + 3600 seconds (1 hour)
  Step 3: HMAC Signature:
          dataToSign = "a1b2c3d4:1720000000:stream:SECRET_SALT"
          signature  = sha256(dataToSign) → "4f3a9b..." (64-char hex)
  Step 4: Payload object:
          {
            uuid: "a1b2c3d4",
            action: "stream",
            source: "https://qu.ax/video.mp4",  ← HIDDEN URL
            filename: "video.mp4",
            expires: 1720000000,
            signature: "4f3a9b..."
          }
  Step 5: Base64 encode → streamToken
  Step 6: streamUrl = "https://worker.dev/fast_stream?token=<base64>"
  Step 7: HTML player inject with streamUrl as <video src>
  Response: { success: true, player_html: "<style>...</style><video>..." }
```

