## 🚨 11. Common Issues & Fixes

| Issue | Cause | Fix |
|---|---|---|
| "Unauthorized Admin" | API token mismatch | Profile se fresh token copy karo |
| "Video not found" | UUID typo | Admin se exact UUID copy karo |
| "Token has expired" | 1 hour purana | Page refresh karo |
| "Invalid Signature" | SECRET_SALT mismatch | Dono jagah same salt set karo |
| Bot ko video dikh rahi | Detection broken | User-Agent check karo |
| "Missing required fields" | Old field names | Hard refresh (Ctrl+Shift+R) |
| Video na chale without fbclid | Social traffic check | URL mein ?fbclid=test add karo |

